headline: Digital Health Tools are Expanding in Scope and Function to Aid Patient Diagnosis, Treatment and Monitoring, Says New Report from The IQVIA Institute
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., December 23, 2024--Despite a drop in venture funding for digital health companies over the last two-and-a-half years, digital health products and solutions are expanding in scope and function to aid patient diagnosis, treatment, and monitoring.
